snippet.title: TEKKEN 3 Jin Kazama Namco System 12 real arcade gameplay 4K 60FPS
snippet.description:
Real arcade hardware recorded on the Elgato Camlink 4K using the OSSC( Not emulated) 
This is not the PlayStation or the Tekken 5 arcade history collection/emulation. I’m using actual arcade hardware.

Game: TEKKEN 3 VER.A (1996)

Arcade System: NAMCO SYSTEM 12


*NOTE: This game play is only for entertainment purposes. Not intended as skill based game play!

Join the Tekken Unchained discord server: https://discord.gg/tekkenunchained

Follow me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fighters_choice_arcade/
